oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Man with camera on cliff
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Man, wearing boots and jumpsuit, with one foot hanging of the cliff, stands with a movie camera on the Black Rock Cliffs on Bald Mountain, at an elevation 4800 feet. The valley is 3300 feet below.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
